name: Illustrated War News, Dec. 23, 1914, page 38, complete, original scan

desc.html:
Images of Darwan Sing Negi and "British Gunners in Action at the Front", from page 38 of the December 23, 1914 Illustrated War News. The individual images are available below.

This is not very accurate colourwise, as with most raw scans; both a copy of the whole page colour-adjusted against the original, and extracted images are available below.
